-- `PATCH /api/extension/sidebars/:id` – Update sidebar name or project
+- `PATCH /api/extension/sidebars/:id` – Update sidebar name or project; empty body refreshes `last_seen` (heartbeat). **`POST`** the same path is accepted if a relay only allows POST.
